Ludwigia helminthorrhiza
is distributed in Central America, Argentina , Mexico , Paraguay , Peru and Venezuela ; Africa and Madagascar ( Campos 2010 ). In Brazil , it is restricted to the states of Bahia , Ceará , Pará , Paraíba and Mato Grosso do Sul , associated to phytogeographic domains of the Amazon, Caatinga and Pantanal (Vieira 2015;
Torres et al . 2016
).
